<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>폼 전송 결과</title>
    <style>
      span {
        color: blue;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= title %> 폼 결과 확인하기</h1>
    <div><span><%= userInfo.name %></span>님 환영합니다!</div>
    <div>성별은<span><%= userInfo.gender %></span></div>
    <div>
      생년월일<span><%= userInfo.birth %></span
      ><span>년 <%= userInfo.month %></span>월
      <span><%= userInfo.days%></span>일!
    </div>
    <div>관심사는<span><%= userInfo.hobby%></span>이군요! 환영합니다!</div>
    <div>
      좋아하는 색상은
      <div
        style="
          width: 100px;
          height: 100px;
          background-color: <%= userInfo.color %>;
        "
      ></div>
    </div>
    <div>좋아하는 숫자는 <span><%= userInfo.grade%></span></div>
  </body>
</html>
